<div class="memorial_instructions">
  <h3> Create a Memorial in a few easy steps. </h3>
  <div id="instruct">
  1. Click the 'Create Memorial' button and enter the person's information. <br>
  <br>
  2. This will take you to the Memorial page where you can upload pictures and invite friends and family to visit. <br>
  <br>
  3. Then go to the Timeline page and upload your memories to be saved in chronological order.
  <br>
